&lt;h2 id="body-text"&gt;Body Text&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is regular body text set in Inter at 18px (1rem) with a line height of 1.618 (the golden ratio). The maximum line width is constrained to 36rem (~65 characters) for optimal readability.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>